{"tid":2432804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新西蘭北島東面海域7.3級強烈地震　預警中心發出海嘯警告","createTime":"2021-03-04T14:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T14:29:41.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae8750591437ab2cf729c48ef4b345164e1bbb1f","tid":2432804,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210304/444263424222826496467120.png/EknmQpqzoKGNRG3w8CWXTQZIW4fwdc1OXBmSR1wZkkc?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210304%2F444263424222826496467120.png%2FEknmQpqzoKGNRG3w8CWXTQZIW4fwdc1OXBmSR1wZkkc%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=c6431bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新西蘭北島東面海域3月4日凌晨發生黎克特制7.3級地震，美國地質調查局（USGS）資料顯示，震源深度僅10公里。<br />\n<br />\n太平洋海嘯預警中心（Pacific Tsunami Warning Center）發出海嘯警告，指這次地震有可能在震央300公里範圍內引發海嘯。<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭國家緊急事務管理局（National Emergency Management Agency）則表示，正在判斷這次7.3級地震會否引發海嘯，將向公眾發布進一步消息。管理局又呼籲任何人若身處感受到強烈地震的海岸邊，應該立即疏散至地勢較高的地區。"},{"pid":"4b7391ede69daa4b052657bc3f8d2177d790d129","tid":2432804,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"支那仲唔快D打救NZ"},{"pid":"cd0fd906c75fb32756aeaebbbc4f68acb0c4ad93","tid":2432804,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"抵死，最好有人死<br />\n奶共丫拿"}]}